Package: shinyfocus
Title: Use Browser Focus Events in 'shiny'
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Jon", "Harmon", , "jonthegeek@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-4781-4346"))
Description: As a user moves through a 'shiny' app, it can be useful to
    trigger server events when different parts of the app gain or lose
    focus. This package aims to make it easy to implement such events.
